OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776708666
OL,3,CEx-Premier League footballer banned
OL,4,Cfrom driving after speeding at 100mph
OL,6,FA former Premier League footballer has
OL,7,Fbeen banned from driving for six
OL,8,Fmonths after being caught speeding at
OL,9,F100mph in a 70mph zone.
OL,11,FIan Poveda, 26, was a Sunderland
OL,12,Fplayer when he was stopped by a police
OL,13,Fofficer who saw him speeding in his
OL,14,Fblack Range Rover on the A184 in South
OL,15,FTyneside around 8.45am on Sunday, 23
OL,16,FFebruary 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
