PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776708666
OL,3,CEx-Premier League footballer banned
OL,4,Cfrom driving after speeding at 100mph
OL,6,FThe winger, who has previously played
OL,7,Ffor Leeds in the Premier League,
OL,8,FBlackburn Rovers, Sheffield Wednesday
OL,9,Fand Blackpool, did not attend the
OL,10,Fhearing at North Tyneside Magistrates'
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FThe London-born Colombia international
OL,14,Fleft Sunderland last month and has
OL,15,Fsigned for Internacional de Bogota.
OL,17,FBrian Payne, prosecuting, told the
OL,18,Fcourt that a police officer saw the
OL,19,FRange Rover accelerate away on the
OL,20,FA184 dual-carriageway.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
