OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776708666
OL,3,CEx-Premier League footballer banned
OL,4,Cfrom driving after speeding at 100mph
OL,6,F"It is clear that the Range Rover was
OL,7,Ftravelling well in excess of the speed
OL,8,Flimit," Mr Payne said.
OL,10,F"I am going to suggest it was at about
OL,11,F100mph in a 70mph zone."
OL,13,FThe officer signalled for the car to
OL,14,Fstop and Poveda pulled over
OL,15,Fimmediately.
OL,17,FJanice Hall, defending, said her
OL,18,Fclient's speeding was "for a very
OL,19,Fshort period of time".
