PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776708666
OL,3,CEx-Premier League footballer banned
OL,4,Cfrom driving after speeding at 100mph
OL,6,FPoveda had nine points on his licence
OL,7,Fat the time after three previous
OL,8,Fspeeding offences, the court heard.
OL,10,FMagistrates banned the player for six
OL,11,Fmonths under the totting up procedure,
OL,12,Fhaving imposed another six points on
OL,13,Fhis licence.
OL,15,FAfter admitting the offence, he was
OL,16,Ffined #800, with a #320 surcharge and
OL,17,F#600 costs.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
